          "virginView": "When you think of an Orlando holiday you think of Walt Disney World, Universal Orlando and the many other theme parks, water parks and attractions that there are to visit. However, you&#x2019;ll be hard pushed to want to leave this hotel with the facilities and activities they have on-site for all the family! A huge resort, with spacious suites that are up to 5 times the size of your average Orlando hotel room, this is perfect for families and groups alike. The suites are complete with kitchen and dining area, for those evenings when you want to chill after a busy day exploring. The Sufari water park is an attraction in it&#x2019;s own right, complete with water slides and a lazy river. There are other swimming pools if you&#x2019;re looking for a more chilled vibe, and whatever pool you&#x2019;re at, you&#x2019;ll never be far away from a bar for refreshments. The activities aren&#x2019;t all water based, there&#x2019;s a huge indoor entertainment centre with arcade games and glow in the dark mini golf, the kids won&#x2019;t know where to start! The resort feels secluded and self-contained, but you&#x2019;re just a five minute drive to shops, restaurants and attractions on Highway 192, and only 10 minutes from Walt Disney World, with a complimentary shuttle bus included to take you to the door and back.",
