          "name": "Disney's All-Star Movies Resort",
          "virginView": "<p>At Disney&#x2019;s All-Star Resorts, larger-than-life sports, music and movie icons surround the rooms as Disney's quality and unique styling is everywhere you look. All three hotels are situated close to the Theme Parks, providing a holiday home for rest and relaxation right in the heart of the action.&#xa0;The stage is set at Disney&#x2019;s All-Star Movies Resort, as massive figures from your favourite Disney movies take a starring role&#x2014; from the dotted pups of 101 Dalmations to the playful toys of Andy&#x2019;s Room. The expansive main pool is inspired by Disney's Fantasia, but if you're looking for something a bit more relaxing - the hockey rink styled pool inspired by The Mighty Ducks film series might be your thing. And the theme continues in the food court as you find yourself in what resembles a grand movie theatre lobby with endless choices to curb your hunger. If being surrounded by Disney movies isn't enough, enjoy watching these films under the stars at night along with campfire activities for all the family to enjoy - a magical way to end the day.&#xa0;</p>",
